{"tid":504024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔真係世界無敵","createTime":"2017-12-19T13:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T17:50:34.000Z","uid":62320,"like":59,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72e2a217d22885f374e0d7a5ced54bfc51d5ee29","tid":504024,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"根本同支那狗無分別 龍門任佢擺<br />\n個韓星死得一兩日 多人悼念有幾出奇<br />\n成班on9仔入去問邊位 唔識你又入？<br />\n一係就話咩韓星死咪死 香港事又唔關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地班鍵國人真係唔覺嘔心架喎 得把口打下字叫關心？<br />\nChester死唔見你地講咩做咩唔關心香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗成個連登既人加埋都唔夠人fans多啦<br />\n你地死呢就真係無人care啦<br />\n<br />\n之於講kpop垃圾真係講到口臭 係佢地眼中得舞曲<br />\n無任何認識就9up盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 韓狗就是罪<br />\n俾你地鍵到國仲衰撚過共產黨啊<br />\n見到成班柒頭毒撚扮哂有品味 <br />\n好有抱負拎關心香港做理由就好想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：負評啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為連登仔駁唔到講句韓狗就係抵死得架啦<br />\n連登仔應該係最嘔心既香港人 影衰香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班心理變態"},{"pid":"3a4936df4fcc1181fdcc0fecd7ea4d96c5ba253e","tid":504024,"uid":62320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"果然駁唔到得負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快啲入黎啦<br />\n世界第一品味既連登仔係邊？<br />\n教大家點聽歌點做人啦"},{"pid":"207af4d1d2021a623cb2af2e2fa54e9d4565cf1d","tid":504024,"uid":62320,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:22:29.000Z","msg":"鍵國撚在哪？好有品味既人又在哪？<br />\n最近唔知聽咩好有soul既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b9c2e1a5378e18175d14799c566cd1935c49d6","tid":504024,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"玩10連都得啦"},{"pid":"11d2d9b61c7764c0ade433ba3416dce79cd01aa1","tid":504024,"uid":54132,"like":6,"dislike":1,"s